ce/Australia_national_netball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mills and Dellavedvoa are arguably still the squad's two best off-the-dribble halfcourt creators, that's not quite a recipe for success.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Boomers will likely need one of their other NBA contributors to step up with strong offensive performances to help supply the offense they need.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.956852282165215e-27, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2024 NBL Finals MVP Jack McVeigh could also provide an offensive boost as well if his shot is falling.\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Boomers do not have a ton of size either.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reath and Landale are both NBA bigs but do not quite provide the backboard dominance you want from starting bigs in FIBA play.\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jock_Landale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Landale\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jock_Landale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jock_Landale\"}, {\"begin\": 1713, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.956852282165215e-27, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two of the